                    How do we use your data?

                    By clicking subscribe, you accept that your e-mail address will be used only to send you Too Faced newsletters and information about Too Faced products, events and offers. You may have the right to review, change or delete your personal data, you can make a request by sending an email to privacy@estee.com. For our contact information click here. You can unsubscribe at any time by clicking on the unsubscribing link in each newsletter. For more information on your ELC Local Entities-Too Faced privacy practices, please see our Privacy Policy.
